MacOS X, Linux, Windows) * Any IDE with Flutter SDK installed (ie. IntelliJ, Android Studio, VSCode etc) * A little knowledge of Dart and Flutter * A brain to think ü§ìü§ì ## ü§ì Author(s) **Olusegun Festus Babajide** [![Twitter Follow](https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/iamjideguru.svg?style=social)](https://twitter.com/iamjideguru) ## Getting Started This project is a starting point for a Flutter application. description: A new Flutter application.

    sdk: flutter

  cupertino_icons: ^0.1.2
